title: typetool from computer arts CD57
content:
dear all, hello's from Dublin

I dug out an old CA mag. with Typetool 1.3 on CD there. It's appearently a full version, though you need to go to a special website and get your serial code from there. Fair enough, but when i log in onto that website I get information that i am not authorised to access it. Is there any catch there? Or is there any other way of retrieving that serial no.?

cheers for any help
